The National President Of the University of Uyo Alumni Association, Hon. Barr. Onofiok Akpan Luke attended the 89th meeting of the Governing Council of the University of uyo, where he represented the convocation. He promised the full cooperation of the Alumni in the task of making the institution one of the best in the country and commended the Prof. Austin Awujo led council and the Prof. Enefiok Essien led management of the institution for their unwavering commitment and dedication to the service of the institution. Thereafter he met with the Alumni Relations officer Mr. Idongesit Nsubong and the staff of the Alumni office. He appealed to the alumni relations officer and staff of the association to cooperate with the new EXCO of the association in the task of building a virile Alumni Association. Courtesy:
Publicity Secretariat
